      "delta": [
        "Baseline: fully serverless, no VPC, no NAT — idle cost ~$0",
        "Single SQS queue + DLQ; eval Lambda triggered from queue (batch=1)",
        "DynamoDB on-demand — absorbs any burst without pre-provisioning",
        "CloudWatch Logs (30d retention) + key alarms (DLQ depth, Lambda error rate) → SNS email",
        "X-Ray tracing on ingest + eval Lambda for cross-service latency visibility",
        "CloudTrail enabled for full API audit"
      ],
      "tradeoffs": [
        "No multi-AZ redundancy — a Lambda cold-start or regional hiccup drops a webhook (best-effort, matches stated tolerance)",
        "Lambda 15-min hard timeout caps eval jobs; very long Python analysis must complete within that window",
        "No dashboard API tier here — downstream read path (public graph/table) must be built separately atop DynamoDB"
      ],
